  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Battlethorne is a third person Conquest game with rpg elements and large scale battles.</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from six weapon classes each with its own unique abilities. Fight across various  large open worlds, conquering bases, gaining loot and vanquishing your foes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight against multiple factions, both human and beast, with over a hundred allies in a four way war.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Six Weapon Classes, each with unique skills</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/b1546a2e34ed4555c2945fc92afcfa74.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/d7b33c6720f5fde9e31cbed48ccbd828.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><u><strong>Warrior/Two handed Axe.</strong></u> Capable of \"zooming/warping\" to targets, knocking the enemy down and lighting enemies on fire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/cae7d7409d0dd69d05aff23ada37c2be.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/ff329cbc8cabed8c57e6803302fa6f81.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><u><strong>Paladin/Sword and Shiled.</strong></u> Puts down a Barrier for for self and allies, pulls targets towards them and can even charges forward knocking down enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/84d94985e2b81eeb87d5b8dcc7089f1f.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/7365742de0e2ad5244f89f0f5570bde8.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><u><strong>Assassin/Daggers.</strong></u> The epitome of guerilla warfare, can go invisible to strike enemies without their knowledge, puts down mines to knock down foes and even </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >has a long range strike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/5dce4fb825072de481eb770bf619a5fe.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/690ba3356204c47ef19d311847b16b7a.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><u><strong>Archer/Bow.</strong></u> The best at long range damage, both single target and AOE(Area of effect). Can chain enemies to the ground not allowing them to move. Also has multishot finishing move for massive damage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/67eb446bf087f7bcc329a940f965c5fd.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/8ca2769dbdebd8daff7cea799eba0797.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><u><strong>Mage/Staff.</strong></u> Heals all allies around him. Crucial for pushing towards the enemy as a group. Can call an ice meteor for AOE damage and also freeze</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >enemies in place if they get too close.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/9db81f6ffd74e0ebd3a22c31f922bdf4.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/a09fa5780fac21872a058190029883dd.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><u><strong>Summoner/Wands.</strong></u> Summons a wolf for single targets and spiders for big AOE blasts. Best of all it can warp/dodge avoiding damage while leaving behind a spirit that attacks enemies if they too get close.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Large scale battles</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight in large scale battles with hundreds of units among four factions, each vying for supremacy across various maps with dozens of Conquest Bases. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your trusty stead to cover large distances in less time and get to the fight quicker.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/0b75f950078e7b3a24f4cc2394a8ead3.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/cbfb4747b02e3a5d1247133a899c6df7.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/46cc6cd2db6976edb49e10f174264f13.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/4947e2c169021669de858bdb00445e8b.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Progression and Loot System</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/af1c150f61abd4938197d1d67eb5d9da.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/a9c26724758e4c3055efb659affd0925.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span>Upgrade your character with loot from your slain enemies and treasure chests strewn across the world. With six armor types, each with their own properties like increased damage, more health to tank and reduced cool-down to make abilities more effective. Six weapon class types each with its own unique abilities, make your own build or change it on the battlefield to suit your play style and objectives. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beasts that fight against everyone on the battlefield.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/f8f1fa79ea14299fd1a859a46fb5fec0.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/d081291cf30a335c678d8a7b30b96d04.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/965a4444f9520181b1fec91f82c16e41.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/8078841e2a5eb26e3bd457ee932dbedb.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/ef8e2a9eea8dcaeecf348d31ef827b14.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/6632d3af1391dc866f7dee0bc6a3c321.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span>Among the four factions are two beast factions that can conquer bases and make others change their strategy in a four way war.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Battlethorne is a third person Conquest game with rpg elements and large scale battles.</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from six weapon classes each with its own unique abilities. Fight across various  large open worlds, conquering bases, gaining loot and vanquishing your foes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight against multiple factions, both human and beast, with over a hundred allies in a four way war.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Six Weapon Classes, each with unique skills</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/b1546a2e34ed4555c2945fc92afcfa74.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/d7b33c6720f5fde9e31cbed48ccbd828.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><u><strong>Warrior/Two handed Axe.</strong></u> Capable of \"zooming/warping\" to targets, knocking the enemy down and lighting enemies on fire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/cae7d7409d0dd69d05aff23ada37c2be.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/ff329cbc8cabed8c57e6803302fa6f81.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><u><strong>Paladin/Sword and Shiled.</strong></u> Puts down a Barrier for for self and allies, pulls targets towards them and can even charges forward knocking down enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/84d94985e2b81eeb87d5b8dcc7089f1f.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/7365742de0e2ad5244f89f0f5570bde8.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><u><strong>Assassin/Daggers.</strong></u> The epitome of guerilla warfare, can go invisible to strike enemies without their knowledge, puts down mines to knock down foes and even </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >has a long range strike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/5dce4fb825072de481eb770bf619a5fe.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/690ba3356204c47ef19d311847b16b7a.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><u><strong>Archer/Bow.</strong></u> The best at long range damage, both single target and AOE(Area of effect). Can chain enemies to the ground not allowing them to move. Also has multishot finishing move for massive damage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/67eb446bf087f7bcc329a940f965c5fd.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/8ca2769dbdebd8daff7cea799eba0797.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><u><strong>Mage/Staff.</strong></u> Heals all allies around him. Crucial for pushing towards the enemy as a group. Can call an ice meteor for AOE damage and also freeze</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >enemies in place if they get too close.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/9db81f6ffd74e0ebd3a22c31f922bdf4.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/a09fa5780fac21872a058190029883dd.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><u><strong>Summoner/Wands.</strong></u> Summons a wolf for single targets and spiders for big AOE blasts. Best of all it can warp/dodge avoiding damage while leaving behind a spirit that attacks enemies if they too get close.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Large scale battles</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight in large scale battles with hundreds of units among four factions, each vying for supremacy across various maps with dozens of Conquest Bases. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your trusty stead to cover large distances in less time and get to the fight quicker.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/0b75f950078e7b3a24f4cc2394a8ead3.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/cbfb4747b02e3a5d1247133a899c6df7.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/46cc6cd2db6976edb49e10f174264f13.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/4947e2c169021669de858bdb00445e8b.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Progression and Loot System</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/af1c150f61abd4938197d1d67eb5d9da.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/a9c26724758e4c3055efb659affd0925.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span>Upgrade your character with loot from your slain enemies and treasure chests strewn across the world. With six armor types, each with their own properties like increased damage, more health to tank and reduced cool-down to make abilities more effective. Six weapon class types each with its own unique abilities, make your own build or change it on the battlefield to suit your play style and objectives. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beasts that fight against everyone on the battlefield.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/f8f1fa79ea14299fd1a859a46fb5fec0.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/d081291cf30a335c678d8a7b30b96d04.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/965a4444f9520181b1fec91f82c16e41.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/8078841e2a5eb26e3bd457ee932dbedb.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/ef8e2a9eea8dcaeecf348d31ef827b14.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615940/extras/6632d3af1391dc866f7dee0bc6a3c321.avif?t=1772008023\" width=308 height=176 /></span>Among the four factions are two beast factions that can conquer bases and make others change their strategy in a four way war.</p>",
